<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="splendid-adj">splendid <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'splendɪd/    美 /'splendɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-magnificent">1.★ <strong>壮丽的；辉煌的；灿烂的 (magnificent)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a splendid castle
金碧辉煌的城堡</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a splendid victory
辉煌的胜利</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>China is a multiethnic country with a long history and a splendid culture.
中国是一个历史悠久、文化灿烂的多民族国家。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-excellent">2.★ <strong>极好的；绝妙的 (excellent)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a splendid idea
绝妙的主意</p></div></div>